exercises.name: pushup
exercises.description: An exercise that primarily works the chest muscles, but also targets the shoulders and arms.

exercises.name: sit up
exercises.description: An abodominal exercise that strengthens your core muscles.

exercises.name: squat
exercises.description: A strength exercise that focuses on the hips and legs.

exercises.name: lunge
exercises.description: A lower body exercise that targets the glutes, hamstrings, and quads.

exercises.name: plank
exercises.description: A bodyweight exercise that focuses on the core, but also strengthens the shoulders, arms, and glutes.

exercises.name: bicep curl
exercises.description: A weight exercise that trains half of your arms, the biceps, by raising weights.

exercises.name: shoulder raise
exercises.description: A weight exercise that trains the deltoid shoulder muscles by raising weights.

exercises.name: chest press
exercises.description: A weight exercise that focuses on the chest muscles, either sitting or laying down, pushing weights away from the chest.

exercises.name: bent over row
exercises.description: A weight exercise that targets back muscles by bending over at an angle and lifting weights towards your body.

exercises.name: tricep extension
exercises.description: A weight exercise that targets half of the arm, pushing your arm from a bent position to a straight position with a weight.

notes.note: Try to take a rest on Sundays!
